article.description: Wayne Arnold had 21 points as Cal State Fullerton defeated Southeast Missouri 64-57 in the Cable Car Classic on Wednesday.
article.headline: Arnold lifts Cal St.-Fullerton over SE Missouri 64-57
article.linkText: Arnold lifts Cal St.-Fullerton over SE Missouri 64-57
article.story: SANTA CLARA, Calif. -- Wayne Arnold had 21 points as Cal State Fullerton defeated Southeast Missouri 64-57 in the Cable Car Classic on Wednesday. Austen Awosika had 13 points and six rebounds for Cal State Fullerton (3-3). Brandon Kamga added six rebounds. Darrious Agnew had 15 points for the Redhawks (2-3). Sage Tolbert added 13 points and 10 rebounds. Alex Caldwell had 11 points. Cal State Fullerton takes on Denver on Friday. Southeast Missouri plays Santa Clara on Friday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
